data.description: Spacious home  boasting over 2200 square feet, offering 4 bedrooms and 2 full baths along with an attached garage in a very  desirable north side location close to the college, shopping, & restaurants;  2 of the bedrooms and 1 bath are on the main floor, the other 2 bedrooms, both boasting walk in closets, along with the other full bathroom, offering double sinks, is upstairs;  Main floor laundry room, large dining room and family room  with french doors leading out to a covered patio, great for entertaining, and a good sized fenced in back yard; Seller to offer a home warranty for buyers peace of mind;  Make your appointment to view this one before it is gone;
